						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying behind the temple of Hanumān.</p>						

						<p>Harihara.</p>						

						<p>This damaged record is in <hi rend="bold">Kannada</hi> and not Telugu as noticed in the <hi rend="italic">Annual Report.</hi> It registers a gift of land in Ṟēvanaūru and mentions the name of the king and a certain <hi rend="bold">Boṁma-nāyaka.</hi></p>						

